id: pm-qd2h
title: "GH-452: plan materialize dead-ends on types with required-on-create custom fields"
description: "Dogfood GH-452: a --required-on-create custom field on a type breaks pm plan materialize for every step (missing_required_option, no passthrough) — the plan->materialize->task loop dead-ends under governed schemas. Duplicate check: searched materialize required field — no existing item."
